# Monitor VMs with Grafana-Prometheus-Node Exporter

Step 1:

Install Docker and Docker Compose 

curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh
sh get-docker.sh

sudo curl -L --fail https://raw.githubusercontent.com/linuxserver/docker-docker-compose/v2/run.sh -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose


Step 2:
sudo -i 
useradd -rs /bin/false prometheus
mkdir /etc/prometheus
touch /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml
mkdir -p /data/prometheus
chown prometheus:prometheus /data/prometheus /etc/prometheus/*

[ copy paste prometheus.yml FILE CONTENTS ]
  
  
 Step 3:
  Create portainer stack  for  docker-compose.yml

    
 Step 4:
 
 import node exporter full
 https://grafana.com/grafana/dashboards/1860
    
